  <brief_title>Inspiratory Muscle Training With Normocapnic Hyperpnea in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of Inspiratory Muscle Training by Means of Spirotiger® in COPD Patients.</official_title>
